First Read: 29-Jan-26
HJR64 Enrolled
1 Enrolled, An Act,
2
3 COMMENDING ANITA HAGGERTY ON THE OCCASION OF HER RETIREMENT
4 AS TALLAPOOSA COUNTY 911 DIRECTOR.
5
6 WHEREAS, with great pride and special pleasure,
7 highest commendations are conveyed to Anita Haggerty on the
8 occasion of her retirement as the Tallapoosa County 911
9 Director after 34 years of dedicated service; and
10 WHEREAS, Anita Haggerty began her career with the
11 county's emergency 911 system on October 1, 1991, before it
12 was up and running; she had been working as a paramedic with
13 East Alabama Medical Center EMS when the 911 board recruited
14 her; her first task was to ensure that every road in the
15 county was named and each resident's address was accurate
16 before the system could go online in 1994, a process that
17 took three years; and
18 WHEREAS, during her tenure, Anita trained hundreds of
19 dispatchers in Public Safety Telecommunications, Emergency
20 Medical Dispatch standards, and CPR; as technology improved
21 over the years, she ensured that Tallapoosa County 911
22 stayed up to date, implementing the Tallapoosa County 911
23 GIS office, as well as the establishment of Enhanced 911
24 (E911), which increased the ease in getting to emergency
25 locations based on cell phone location among other essential
26 improvements; and
27 WHEREAS, noting how difficult it is to depart from a
28 job you truly love and that you built from the ground up,
Page 1

job you truly love and that you built from the ground up,
HJR64 Enrolled
29 Anita will return as a part-time employee in February 2026;
30 she is the example of kindness, dedication, and integrity,
31 and her work has made Tallapoosa County a safer place to
32 live; now therefore,
33 BE IT RESOLVED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA, BOTH
34 HOUSES THEREOF CONCURRING, That Anita Haggerty is highly
35 commended on her 34-year career with Tallapoosa County 911,
36 culminating in her esteemed leadership as its director, and
37 this resolution is offered to her as evidence of our high
38 regard and sincere gratitude, with best wishes for many
39 blessings and prosperity, even as she continues to support
40 the agency in a part-time capacity.
